statements.sql: select `tbl_client`.*, (select count(*) from `tbl_client_prog` where `tbl_client`.`id` = `tbl_client_prog`.`client_id` and `prog_running_status` in (0, 1, 2) and exists (select * from `tbl_prog` where `tbl_client_prog`.`prog_id` = `tbl_prog`.`prog_id` and exists (select * from `tbl_main_prog` where `tbl_prog`.`main_prog_id` = `tbl_main_prog`.`id` and `prog_name` = 'Admissions Mentoring'))) as `client_program_count`, (select count(*) from `tbl_client_prog` where `tbl_client`.`id` = `tbl_client_prog`.`client_id` and `prog_running_status` = 2 and exists (select * from `tbl_prog` where `tbl_client_prog`.`prog_id` = `tbl_prog`.`prog_id` and exists (select * from `tbl_main_prog` where `tbl_prog`.`main_prog_id` = `tbl_main_prog`.`id` and `prog_name` = 'Admissions Mentoring'))) as `client_program_finish_count` from `tbl_client` where exists (select * from `tbl_client_prog` where `tbl_client`.`id` = `tbl_client_prog`.`client_id` and `prog_running_status` in (2)) having client_program_count = client_program_finish_count

select `tbl_department`.*, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`department_id` as `pivot_department_id`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`user_type_id` as `pivot_user_type_id`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`start_date` as `pivot_start_date`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`end_date` as `pivot_end_date`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`status` as `pivot_status`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`updated_at` as `pivot_updated_at` from `tbl_department` inner join `tbl_user_type_detail` on `tbl_department`.`id` = `tbl_user_type_detail`.`department_id` where `tbl_user_type_detail`.`user_id` = 24
select count(*) as aggregate from `tbl_roles` inner join `tbl_user_roles` on `tbl_roles`.`id` = `tbl_user_roles`.`role_id` where `tbl_user_roles`.`user_id` = 24 and `role_name` = 'admin'

select count(*) as aggregate from (select `client`.*, `parent`.`mail` as `parent_mail`, `parent`.`phone` as `parent_phone`, RTRIM(CONCAT(parent.first_name, " ", COALESCE(parent.last_name, ""))) as parent_name from `client` left join `tbl_client_relation` as `relation` on `relation`.`child_id` = `client`.`id` left join `tbl_client` as `parent` on `parent`.`id` = `relation`.`parent_id` where exists (select * from `tbl_client_prog` where `client`.`id` = `tbl_client_prog`.`client_id` and exists (select * from `tbl_prog` where `tbl_client_prog`.`prog_id` = `tbl_prog`.`prog_id` and exists (select * from `tbl_main_prog` where `tbl_prog`.`main_prog_id` = `tbl_main_prog`.`id` and `prog_name` = 'Admissions Mentoring')) and `status` = 1 and `prog_running_status` != 2) and exists (select * from `tbl_roles` inner join `tbl_client_roles` on `tbl_roles`.`id` = `tbl_client_roles`.`role_id` where `client`.`id` = `tbl_client_roles`.`client_id` and `role_name` = 'student') and `client`.`st_statusact` = 1 order by `first_name` asc) count_row_table

select `client`.*, `parent`.`mail` as `parent_mail`, `parent`.`phone` as `parent_phone`, RTRIM(CONCAT(parent.first_name, " ", COALESCE(parent.last_name, ""))) as parent_name from `client` left join `tbl_client_relation` as `relation` on `relation`.`child_id` = `client`.`id` left join `tbl_client` as `parent` on `parent`.`id` = `relation`.`parent_id` where exists (select * from `tbl_client_prog` where `client`.`id` = `tbl_client_prog`.`client_id` and exists (select * from `tbl_prog` where `tbl_client_prog`.`prog_id` = `tbl_prog`.`prog_id` and exists (select * from `tbl_main_prog` where `tbl_prog`.`main_prog_id` = `tbl_main_prog`.`id` and `prog_name` = 'Admissions Mentoring')) and `status` = 1 and `prog_running_status` != 2) and exists (select * from `tbl_roles` inner join `tbl_client_roles` on `tbl_roles`.`id` = `tbl_client_roles`.`role_id` where `client`.`id` = `tbl_client_roles`.`client_id` and `role_name` = 'student') and `client`.`st_statusact` = 1 order by `first_name` asc, `full_name` asc limit 10 offset 0
